Flutter & Firebase: Build a Complete App for iOS & Android 

If you are a flutter enthusiast, we recommend you to follow this beginner friendly course by Andrea Bizzotto! 🤩📚✅

Flutter is a mobile framework by Google for building beautiful and fast native apps. Flutter is very productive and offers a rich set of widgets that makes building apps a breeze. Once you experience hot-reload and everything else Flutter has to offer, you will never want to go back. 🙅🏻‍♀️💯

In this course you will build a complete, real-world application for iOS and Android, by using Dart, Flutter and Firebase. 📲💻

💡Good News? 

You will get lifetime access. 🤩 This course starts from the basics, and includes a full introduction to Dart and Flutter. This means that NO prior experience with Dart and mobile app development is needed. 😇🤝🏻


